"attributes": {"content": "  古時，尚蜀山巒，人力不能及。", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  蜀道難，難於上青天。", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......如今不同了。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可再如何不同，有些事情，不變就是不變的。", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  三山十七峰，處處尋不得。梁大人還要再找嗎？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  得找。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不惜瞞天過海，騙過我，騙過所有人也得找？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#7$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  得找的。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  為什麼？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你難道不知道，縱使有千番道理，逾矩便是逾矩，犯忌便是犯忌？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#5$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你難道不知道，此事出了一點差池，別說前程不保，論起罪責，你首當其衝？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#5$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#6$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你難道不知道......我是願意聽你說的？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#6$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我知道。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以我更不能告訴你。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......為何？", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#4$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  因為梁某人身為一城之知府，只考慮一城之安危性命。一磚一瓦，一爐一灶，但凡有絲毫損毀，便是我的失職。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  上峰齟齬，梁某人所能做的......唯有勉力而行而已。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......早年初會尚蜀，見你雖偶爾固執古板，但畢竟剛正不阿，一身正氣。我一直堅信，你我共事，定能跨過千難萬阻。", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#6$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可如今......", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#6$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我卻難免有些失望。", "name": "寧小姐"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......這句話......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是作為梁某人的朋友寧小姐提醒梁某人呢......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#2$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_298_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_295_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......還是作為朝廷從二品欽差大員，禮部左侍郎寧辭秋，敲打梁某人的？", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#5$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}